org.svvrl.goal.cmd

Class SetStmt

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.svvrl.goal.cmd.SetStmt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Statement

    public class SetStmt
extends java.lang.Object
implements Statement
    A SetStmt assigns a value to an l-value. If there is no l-value in the SetStmt, the value will be printed as a string.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
